text: The 1946 Kansas gubernatorial election was held on November 5, 1946. Republican nominee Frank Carlson defeated Democratic nominee Harry Hines Woodring with 53.50% of the vote. ==General election== ===Candidates=== Major party candidates *Frank Carlson, Republican *Harry H. Woodring, Democratic Other candidates *David C. White, Prohibition *Harry Graber, Socialist ===Results=== ==References== Gubernatorial 1946 Kansas
title: 1946 Kansas gubernatorial election
